<DIV>The solution is not removing the flagging system but rather do away with the huge death penalties, removing the no drops making everything tradable, and making alternate ways for smaller groups to get flagged. If you own the expansions and have the appropriate level, you should be able to reap their rewards no matter what your playing style. SOE should make gear level appropriate but remove the no drop part. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
